310
00:31:30,223 --> 00:31:34,081
What about you? You seem to like eating ginger like old people.

311
00:31:35,528 --> 00:31:36,449
No.

312
00:31:39,926 --> 00:31:41,315
I like old people.

313
00:31:55,812 --> 00:31:56,795
