323
00:35:24,789 --> 00:35:25,507
Uncle Jim!

324
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:27,892
What?

325
00:35:28,025 --> 00:35:30,466
You’re dreamy like a teen waiting for a text back from his lover.

326
00:35:30,466 --> 00:35:31,882
Do you want me to put a date on the beer?

327
00:35:32,891 --> 00:35:33,665
