345
00:37:15,792 --> 00:37:17,792
Here’s your chic… Oh shit!

346
00:37:28,356 --> 00:37:29,373
What the hell was that?

347
00:37:34,801 --> 00:37:36,496
I don’t understand.

348
00:37:36,691 --> 00:37:37,955
