352
00:38:06,602 --> 00:38:08,036
Hey, Leng.

353
00:38:10,705 --> 00:38:11,983
Need my help?

354
00:38:14,982 --> 00:38:15,839
Why are you here?

355
00:38:16,506 --> 00:38:19,006
Can I have the diner’s spare key? I didn’t bring it with me last night.

356
00:38:23,321 --> 00:38:24,031
Thank you.

357
00:38:24,031 --> 00:38:24,987
Where’s Uncle Jim?

358
00:38:30,496 --> 00:38:32,207
Come home as soon as school is over.Come home as soon as school is over.

359
00:38:32,728 --> 00:38:34,073
I don’t want to hear your uncle nag.

360
00:38:35,519 --> 00:38:36,930
Let him.

361
00:38:38,141 --> 00:38:39,310
He stops when he’s done with it.

362
00:38:40,511 --> 00:38:41,920
Like uncle, like nephew.

363
00:38:46,619 --> 00:38:47,636
Hey, Leng.

364
00:38:48,771 --> 00:38:52,112
