519
00:52:19,829 --> 00:52:21,829
And I look so damn tired.

520
00:52:21,829 --> 00:52:23,761
You must see it yourself for once.

521
00:52:27,953 --> 00:52:29,953
I take that as your permission.

522
00:52:32,168 --> 00:52:35,872
