528
00:53:04,031 --> 00:53:06,031
I don't believe you have no friends.

529
00:53:07,710 --> 00:53:09,710
I do have some.

530
00:53:09,986 --> 00:53:13,953
But it's more about who I'd like to drink with.

531
00:53:46,722 --> 00:53:48,098
This is yours.

532
00:53:48,098 --> 00:53:49,788
You dropped it the other night.

533
00:54:01,663 --> 00:54:03,663
